4-9af040d4/forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:142:where `<class-key>` is a sanitized form of the dynamic-access class the\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5184-9af040d4/forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:284:The module must not depend on any workflow strategy or intervention.\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5184-9af040d4/forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:398:`codex_then_pi` lives with each strategy spec:\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5184-9af040d4/forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:402:| Dynamic-access workflow | [dynamic-access-workflow.md](dynamic-access-workflow.md) |\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/tests/test_large_library_progress.py:43:                strategy_name=\"dynamic_access_main_sources_pi_gpt-5.5\",\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/tests/test_large_library_progress.py:68:                strategy_name=\"coverage_only_pi_gpt-5.5\",\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/tests/test_large_library_progress.py:85:                strategy_name=\"dynamic_access_main_sources_pi_gpt-5.5\",\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/tests/test_large_library_progress.py:95:                strategy_name=\"dynamic_access_main_sources_pi_gpt-5.5\",\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5184-9af040d4/forge/docs/dynamic-access-strategy.md:1:# Dynamic-access strategy internals (current PR)\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge6/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5184-9af040d4/forge/docs/dynamic-access-strategy.md:6:  - `main(...)`: integrates source-context setup into the add-library workflow by calling `populate_artifact_ur